{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/preview-anime-musim-panas-2018-kyoto-teramachi-sanjo-no-holmes/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Preview Anime Musim Panas 2018: Kyoto Teramachi Sanjo no Holmes","content":"<p>Dalam anime, cerita bertema detektif terkenal seperti Conan, Kindaichi, ataupun grup detektif yang ada di Dan Detective School biasanya menceritakan pemecahan kejadian aneh di berbagai area, tak hanya di satu tempat saja. Namun bagaimana dengan cerita detektif yang memecahkan kasus-kasus di wilayah sekitarnya?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48568\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48568\" data-attachment-id=\"48568\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/preview-anime-musim-panas-2018-kyoto-teramachi-sanjo-no-holmes/attachment/kyoto1/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto1.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"kyoto1\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Versi Manga dari Kyoto Teramachi Sanjo no Holmes (Sumber: natalie.mu)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto1-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto1.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48568\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto1.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto1-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48568\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Versi Manga dari Kyoto Teramachi Sanjo no Holmes (Sumber: natalie.mu)</p></div></p>\n<p>Jawabannya ada di Kyoto Teramachi Sanjo no Holmes. Bertempat di toko barang antik yang berada di salah satu distrik perbelanjaan di kota Kyoto, Teramachi Sanjo, seorang gadis remaja kelas 2 SMA bernama Aoi Mashiro tanpa sengaja bertemu dengan Kiyotaka Yagashira, anak dari pemilik toko. Aoi lalu bekerja sambilan di toko barang antik itu.</p>\n<p>Aoi, yang jujur, memiliki intuisi bagus, dan pintar menilai orisinalitas suatu barang, dibutuhkan kemampuannya oleh Kiyotaka yang sedang mempelajari nilai dari suatu barang. Kiyotaka, yang terkenal dengan sebutan Holmes-nya Teramachi Sanjo, menyelesaikan berbagai kasus yang ada di wilayah distrik perbelanjaan Teramachi Sanjo dengan dibantu oleh Aoi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48569\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48569\" data-attachment-id=\"48569\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/preview-anime-musim-panas-2018-kyoto-teramachi-sanjo-no-holmes/attachment/kyoto2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"kyoto2\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Poster Anime Kyoto Teramachi Sanjo no Holmes (Sumber: natalie.mu)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48569\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48569\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Poster Anime Kyoto Teramachi Sanjo no Holmes (Sumber: natalie.mu)</p></div></p>\n<p>Anime ini diadaptasi dari serial novel misteri terkenal di Jepang berjudul sama yang ditulis oleh Mai Mochizuki dan ilustrator Yamochisizu. Novel ini pertama kali dirilis oleh penerbit Futabasha pada April 2015 hingga edisi ke-9 pada Maret 2018 lalu. Novel ini pernah memenangkan penghargaan dari Kyoto Book Grand Prix pada tahun 2016 lalu.</p>\n<p>Adaptasi ke dalam bentuk manga pun dibuat dengan dibantu oleh Ichiha Akizuki yang diserialisasikan majalah manga Monthly Action penerbit Futabasha sejak Desember 2017 lalu. Proyek pembuatan anime ini sudah dimulai ketika<em> website</em> resminya mengumumkan kalau  adaptasi anime yang akan diproduksi oleh studio Seven dan akan memulai penayangannya pada 9 Juli 2018 mendatang.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48570\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48570\" data-attachment-id=\"48570\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/preview-anime-musim-panas-2018-kyoto-teramachi-sanjo-no-holmes/attachment/kyoto3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"kyoto3\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Papan nama toko barang antik milik Kiyotaka (Sumber: youtube.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48570\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48570\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Papan nama toko barang antik milik Kiyotaka (Sumber: youtube.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Dipimpin oleh Noriyoshi Sasaki sebagai sutradara, yang sebelumnya pernah terlibat di anime Okusama ga Seitokaichou, King’s Game, dan Ojisan to Marshmallow, dibantu oleh Kenichi Yamashita sebagai penanggung jawab naskah serial anime ini. Selain itu, Noriyoshi juga kembali bekerja sama dengan Yosuke Ito yang akan mendesain karakter dan pengarah animasi utama, setelah sebelumnya mereka sempat bekerja sama di King’s Game.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48571\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48571\" data-attachment-id=\"48571\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/preview-anime-musim-panas-2018-kyoto-teramachi-sanjo-no-holmes/attachment/kyoto4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"kyoto4\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Interior toko barang antik (Sumber: youtube.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48571\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48571\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Interior toko barang antik (Sumber: youtube.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Pengisi suaranya ada Miyu Tomita, pengisi suara muda bertalenta yang pernah mengisi suara karakter di Gabriel DropOut, Made in Abyss, dan Aikatsu Stars, yang akan mengisi suara karakter Aoi Mashiro. Sementara itu, yang mengisi suara karakter Kiyotaka Yagashira adalah Kaito Ishikawa, yang sebelumnya mengisi suara di berbagai anime terkenal seperti Haikyu, Tokyo Ghoul, One Punch Man, My Hero Academia, dan masih banyak lagi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48572\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48572\" data-attachment-id=\"48572\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/preview-anime-musim-panas-2018-kyoto-teramachi-sanjo-no-holmes/attachment/kyoto5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"kyoto5\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Kiyotaka Yagashira (Sumber: youtube.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48572\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48572\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Kiyotaka Yagashira (Sumber: youtube.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Beberapa pengisi suara karakter pendukung juga telah diumumkan. Ryohei Kimura akan mengisi suara Akihito Kajiwara, aktor pemula yang tampan, anak dari penulis novel terkenal yang selalu terlibat konflik dengan Kiyotaka. Ada pula Koji Yusa sebagai Ensho, seorang penipu ulung yang selalu mengenakan kimono dan pernah memiliki keinginan untuk menjadi biksu, tetapi dia kembali ke pekerjaannya semula berkat bertemu dengan Kiyotaka. Selain itu, ada pula Sanae Kobayashi yang mengisi karakter Rikyu Takiyama, remaja tampan yang respek kepada Kiyotaka namun keras kepada Aoi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_48573\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-48573\" data-attachment-id=\"48573\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/preview-anime-musim-panas-2018-kyoto-teramachi-sanjo-no-holmes/attachment/kyoto6/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto6.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"kyoto6\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Aoi Mashiro (Sumber: youtube.com)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto6-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto6.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-48573\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto6.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/kyoto6-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-48573\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Aoi Mashiro (Sumber: youtube.com)</p></div></p>\n<p>Wagakki Band yang membawakan lagu Sasameyuki sebagai lagu tema dan AOP yang membawakan lagu pembuka berjudul Koi ni Saku Nazo, Harahara to menjadi penambah daya tarik anime ini. Penasaran dengan lagunya? Simak sekaligus dengan video promosinya berikut:</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/gsSTI1d7NLM\" width=\"560\" height=\"315\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\"></iframe></p>\n<p>Karena anime ini bukan merupakan anime dengan seri panjang seperti Conan dan Kindaichi, kalian bisa menikmatinya selagi ada waktu luang. Lagipula, memecahkan suatu misteri yang disajikan tentu butuh ketepatan berpikir dan analisa, bukan?</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"a356e250-5bfd-518b-b10d-2a43fa4b811f"}}}